title: Pink Cherry Complex
alternative_title: Cherry Boy Complex ; ピンクチェリーコンプレックス
status: Cherry Boy Complex ; ピンクチェリーコンプレックス
description:
Description :
        Uber popular high school student Ren has a secret he doesn't want anyone to discover, and it's that his cherry has yet to be popped! One day, his super cool and handsome friend Sousuke asks to watch an adult film together, where Sousuke finds out the truth about Ren. Sousuke suggests that he let Ren "practice" on him, so he's ready for his next girlfriend. Thus marks the start of Megane's long awaited new series!!
